text: Cloniocerus ochripennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1940. It is known from Tanzania.BioLib.cz - Cloniocerus ochripennis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1940
